      <div class="msgContentFrame">You're making the wrong things.  Sand is worthless.  Jewelry is the way to go, especially if your server is getting a lot of new players that need things like copper wristlets.  It won't be fast money like that armorer with a bronze haubergon, but it is a steady stream if you price your bazaar and retainer right. <br /> <br />And don't be afraid to risk a higher synth, afaik bone rings are 9 or 10 so you should be able to make 85%ish of your attempts.  No risk = no reward.</div>
