      <div class="msgContentFrame">Take a pickaxe, set your elements attribute to mainly wind and go dig some holes. Bonechip, copper ore and wind shard aplenty <br />From there, copper nuggets (need maybe 10 fire cristal and your set for copper), some ingots (get some from lvl1-5 goldsmith leve too), = copper based jewelry <br />bonechip -&gt; bone ring and harpoon butt (then NPC most of it ^^), windshard are wasted that way, but it's fast, and your not paying for those shards remember :) <br />you will be 10+ in no time. From there the route I took was more jewelry, some precious stones, leve and brass nuggets/ingot until 15, then some brass jewelry, a bit more copper jewelry, some weapons, more leve and some silver nuggets/ingot down the road to 19 where I stand. <br /> <br />slow, steady and profitable (I mean I have stacks and stacks of brass/silver nuggets I'm hoarding for later, If I were to sell those it would be profitable). Need tons of fire cristals to work though (and mining is a good plus) <br />Just to give you an idea, yesterday I went through about 100 fire cristals (bought 60 and farmed 40 myself, long day ^^) <br /> <br />there maybe some faster path, but I like mine since I'm a miner.</div>
