      <div class="msgContentFrame">Mining and Goldsmithing just go together. It's insane for someone to take up Armorer, Blacksmithing, or Goldsmithing without being a Miner as well. You're going to waste so much money. I've hardly spent a dime on my craft, but I've gotten it to 15 with little resistance. If you don't take up mining, you're going to be spending A LOT of money with very little turn around. <div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>FFXIV (Joscerelle Faire) <br />Goldsmith20, Mining18, Archer15 <br />I wear pink... that's what I do. <br /> <br />FFXI (Retired) <br />SMN75, BLM54, WHM40, BRD31, PLD25, <br />Cooking 100+2, Clothcraft 40 <br />Sellius (MULE) Clothcraft 61, Leathercraft 20, Goldsmithing 12 <br /></div></div>
